OL,3,CVictim named in Horbury murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FA woman whose death is being treated
OL,7,Fas murder has been named by police.
OL,9,FCarolann Barraclough, 37, was found
OL,10,Fdead at a property on Ken Church
OL,11,FDrive, Horbury, on Thursday 5 March.
OL,13,FPolice attended the property after
OL,14,Fthey received reports raising concern
OL,15,Ffor a woman's safety.
OL,17,FA 45-year-old man, who was arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of her murder yesterday,
OL,19,Fremains in police custody
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
