OL,3,CVictim named in Horbury murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Stacey Atkinson, of the
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire Police Homicide and
OL,8,FMajor Enquiry Team, said: "Complex
OL,9,Fenquiries remain ongoing at Ken
OL,10,FChurchill Drive and will be for a
OL,11,Fnumber of days as we investigate what
OL,12,Fhas taken place there.
OL,14,F"Work to formally ID the woman found
OL,15,Fat the address remains ongoing, but we
OL,16,Fdo think it is Carolann, and specially
OL,17,Ftrained officers continue to support
OL,18,Fher family.
OL,26,@pD@[OUvD@AOU
